### List tasks with response envelope
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/tasks?limit=2&offset=0
X-API-Key: dev-secret-key

### Count respects status filter
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/tasks?status=completed&limit=1&offset=0
X-API-Key: dev-secret-key

### Failed-task count uses the same filter
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/tasks?status=failed&limit=1&offset=0
X-API-Key: dev-secret-key
